OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,FSingle bus fares across England will
OL,8,Fbe capped at #2 from January, Prime
OL,9,FMinister Andy Burnham has announced,
OL,10,Fafter he pledged to to lead a "cost-of-
OL,11,Fliving government" in his first
OL,12,FCabinet meeting.
OL,14,FThe nationwide cap is currently set at
OL,15,F#3 until the end of March 2027,
OL,16,Falthough some areas, including London
OL,17,Fand Greater Manchester, where Burnham
OL,18,Fset a #2 limit as mayor, have lower
OL,19,Ftop rates for single tickets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,FBurnham said: "Good, affordable
OL,8,Ftransport links are essential. No one
OL,9,Fshould be priced out of those and left
OL,10,Fbehind.
OL,12,F"But for too long people have said
OL,13,Fthat cheaper transport isn't an
OL,14,Foption. I don't accept that. I've done
OL,15,Fit before and I will do it again now:
OL,16,FA #2 cap on bus fares for millions
OL,17,Facross the country.
OL,26,@oD@OOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,F"Lower fares will help people get to
OL,8,Fwhere they need to, giving them
OL,9,Fbreathing space to help with the cost
OL,10,Fof living."
OL,12,FThe measure is backed by #454 million
OL,13,Fof funding, including money to allow
OL,14,Fdevolved governments to take similar
OL,15,Faction.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,FSome #400 million of that funding will
OL,8,Fcome from switching investment in
OL,9,Finternational climate finance to
OL,10,Floans, with the rest from savings in
OL,11,Fthe Department for Energy Security and
OL,12,FNet Zero budget.
OL,14,FThe total cost of the scheme is
OL,15,Fexpected to be more than #500 million,
OL,16,Fwith the rest coming from Department
OL,17,Ffor Transport funding already
OL,18,Fallocated to buses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,FA #2 cap had been in place between
OL,8,FJanuary 2023 and December 2024, but
OL,9,Fthe incoming Labour administration
OL,10,Fargued it was not affordable, although
OL,11,Fsome metro mayors, including Burnham,
OL,12,Fdecided to fund an extension of the
OL,13,Flower limit in their areas.
OL,15,FChancellor John Healey said "millions
OL,16,Fof people" would benefit from fares
OL,17,Fbeing slashed by a third and insisted
OL,18,Fthe measure could be paid for.
OL,26,@wD@]OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
