FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,F"This action to ease the cost of
OL,8,Fliving is funded by savings made
OL,9,Felsewhere, so there's no burden to
OL,10,FBritish taxpayers, just pounds going
OL,11,Fback into their pockets," he said.
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,14,Fsaid the move would make "everyday
OL,15,Fjourneys easier and cheaper".
