OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784772170
OL,3,CAndy Burnham unveils #2 bus fare cap
OL,4,Cin pledge to be 'cost-of-living
OL,5,Cgovernment'
OL,7,FThe announcement is the latest in a
OL,8,Fseries of measures the new prime
OL,9,Fminister says he intends to announce
OL,10,Fto give the British public "breathing
OL,11,Fspace" in managing their finances.
OL,13,FIn his first cabinet meeting on
OL,14,FTuesday, Burnham told his ministers he
OL,15,Fwould lead a "cost-of-living"
OL,16,Fgovernment, and give people a "sense
OL,17,Fthat help is coming".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
